    "SUMMARY": "Naif Abdulraheem Al-Hadhrami (Arabic: نايف عبدالرحيم الحضرمي; born 18 July 2001) is a Qatari professional footballer who plays as a midfielder for Qatari club Al Shahaniya, on loan from Al-Rayyan and the Qatar national football team.\nAl-Hadhrami represented the Qatar national team in the 2022 FIFA World Cup that was hosted in his home country Qatar."
